    "nome": "caracteristicas-operacao",
    "conteudo": "<div style=\" padding: 0mm 4mm;\">\n  <div style=\"border-top: 1px solid #000\">\n    <b style=\"font-size: 14pt\">II - Características da Operação</b>\n  </div>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse\">\n    <tr style=\" border-top: 1px solid black\">\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black; width: 33%\">\n        1 - Valor do Crédito <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_valor_credito_liberado}}</p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black; width: 33%\">\n        1.1 - Valor Total do Empréstimo <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_valor_total_emprest}}</p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; width: 33%\">\n        1.2 - Prazo da Operação <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_prazo_operacao}}</p>\n      </th>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse\">\n    <tr style=\" border-top: 1px solid black\">\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; width: 33%\">\n        3 - Encargos Prefixados\n      </th>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse\">\n    <tr style=\" border-top: 1px solid black\">\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black; width: 25%\">\n        3.1 - Taxa de Juros Efetiva <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_taxa_juros_efetiva_mes}} % ao mês</p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black; width: 25%\">\n        3.2 - Taxa de Juros Efetiva <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_taxa_juros_efetiva_ano}} % ao ano</p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black ; width: 25%\">\n        4 - Periodicidade Capitalização <p style=\"margin: 0\"><b style=\"font-size: 14pt\"> Diária </b></p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; width: 25%\">\n        5 - Valor do IOF <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_valor_iof}}</p>\n      </th>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse\">\n    <tr style=\" border-top: 1px solid black\">\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black; width: 25%\">\n        6 - Valor da(s) tarifa(s) <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_valor_tarifa}}</p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black; width: 25%\">\n        7 - Quantidade Parcelas <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_qtd_parcelas}}</p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black ; width: 25%\">\n        8 - Valor da(s) Parcela(s) <p style=\"margin: 0\">em R${{ccb_cpinvest_valor_parcelas}}</p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; width: 25%\">\n        8.1 - Valor Total da(s) Parcelas <p style=\"margin: 0\">em R${{ccb_cpinvest_valor_total_parcelas}}</p>\n      </th>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse\">\n    <tr style=\" border-top: 1px solid black\">\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black; width: 50%\">\n        9 - Periodicidade Pagamento da(s) Parcela(s) <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_periodicidade_pagamento}}</p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; width: 50%\">\n        10 - Encargos Moratórios <p style=\"margin: 0\"><b style=\"font-size: 14pt\"> (Vide Cláusula 5 do Quadro VI) </b></p>\n      </th>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n  <table style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse\">\n    <tr style=\" border-top: 1px solid black\">\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black; width: 33%\">\n        11 - Praça de Pagamento <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_praca_pagamento}}</p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; border-right: 1px solid black; width: 33%\">\n        12 - Vencto. da 1ª. Parcela <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_vencimento_primeira_parcela}}</p>\n      </th>\n      <th style=\"text-align: left; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; width: 33%\">\n        13- Vencto. da Última Parcela <p style=\"margin: 0\">{{ccb_cpinvest_vencimento_ultima_parcela}}</p>\n      </th>\n    </tr>\n  </table>\n</div>\n",
